ed to each value (e.g. `%` or ` ms`).\\\"}},\\\"additionalProperties\\\":false,\\\"description\\\":\\\"Number-formatting settings for the values on this axis or series.\\\"}},\\\"additionalProperties\\\":false,\\\"description\\\":\\\"Optional series settings. Only applies to Y-axis series.\\\"}},\\\"required\\\":[\\\"column\\\"],\\\"additionalProperties\\\":false},\\\"description\\\":\\\"One or more numeric columns plotted as Y series.\\\"}},\\\"additionalProperties\\\":false,\\\"description\\\":\\\"Chart configuration. Ignored when `display` is `ActionsTable` or `BoldNumber`.\\\"},\\\"display\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"enum\\\":[\\\"ActionsTable\\\",\\\"BoldNumber\\\",\\\"ActionsLineGraph\\\",\\\"ActionsBar\\\",\\\"ActionsPie\\\",\\\"ActionsStackedBar\\\",\\\"ActionsAreaGraph\\\",\\\"TwoDimensionalHeatmap\\\"],\\\"description\\\":\\\"Visualization type. Defaults to `ActionsTable` when omitted.\\\\n\\\\nGuidance:\\\\n- Single-value result (one numeric column, one row) → `BoldNumber`.\\\\n- Time series → `ActionsLineGraph` or `ActionsAreaGraph`.\\\\n- Categorical proportions → `ActionsPie`.\\\\n- Categorical comparison → `ActionsBar` or `ActionsStackedBar`.\\\\n- Two-dimensional aggregation → `TwoDimensionalHeatmap`.\\\\n- Otherwise → `ActionsTable`.\\\"},\\\"kind\\\":{\\\"default\\\":\\\"DataVisualizationNode\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"const\\\":\\\"DataVisualizationNode\\\"},\\\"source\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"object\\\",\\\"propertyNames\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\"},\\\"additionalProperties\\\":{},\\\"description\\\":\\\"HogQL query object that produces the rows to visualize.\\\"},\\\"tableSettings\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"object\\\",\\\"properties\\\":{\\\"columns\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"array\\\",\\\"items\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"object\\\",\\\"properties\\\":{\\\"column\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Name of a column returned by the SQL query to map onto this axis.\\\"},\\\"settings\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"object\\\",\\\"pr